  function openPopup() {
    setTimeout(function() {
      $("#arc-access-popup").fadeIn();
      $("html").css("overflow", "hidden");
    }, 1000);
  }  
  
  $(window).load(function() {
    
    if (Modernizr.mq('only screen and (min-width: 800px)')) {

      var visited = Cookies.get('visited');
  
      if (visited == 'yes') {
        return false;
      } else {
        openPopup();
      }
  
      Cookies.set('visited', 'yes', { expires: 31, path: '' }); 

      $('.popup-close, #arc-access-popup a').click(function() {
        $("#arc-access-popup").fadeOut();
        $("html").css("overflow", "visible"); 
      });
    
      $('#arc-access-popup a').magnificPopup({
        disableOn: 800,
        type: 'iframe'
      });
      
    }
    
});

       <script type="text/javascript">
        var audioFunctions = new Array();
    var videoFunctions = new Array();


    function makeJPlayer(audioId, elid, mediaUrl, title)
    {
        var plh = $('#' + elid);
        var source = $('#jplayer-template').html();
        var template = Handlebars.compile(source);
        var context = { id: audioId, title: title };
        var html = template(context);

        plh.append(html);

        $("#jquery_jplayer_" + audioId).jPlayer({
            preload: "none",
            ready: function ()
            {
                $(this).jPlayer("setMedia", {
                    mp3: mediaUrl
                });
            },
            play: function ()
            {
                $(this).jPlayer("pauseOthers");
            },
            swfPath: "/templates/arc/swf/",
            supplied: "mp3",
            smoothPlayBar: true,
            cssSelectorAncestor: "#jp_container_" + audioId
        });
    }



    function makeVideoPlayer(newsItemID, elid, mediaUrl)
    {
        var plh = $('#' + elid);
        var source = $('#jplayer-template-video').html();
        var template = Handlebars.compile(source);
        var videoID = youtube_parser(mediaUrl);
        var context = { id: newsItemID, link: mediaUrl, videoID: videoID };
        var html = template(context);

        plh.append(html);

    }


    
    function youtube_parser(url){
        var regExp = /^.*((youtu.be\/)|(v\/)|(\/u\/\w\/)|(embed\/)|(watch\?))\??v?=?([^#\&\?]*).*/;
        var match = url.match(regExp);
        return (match&&match[7].length==11)? match[7] : false;
    }


    $(window).load(function() {
        $('.video-container a').on('click', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            var videoURL = $(this).attr('href');
            $(this).hide();
            $(this).next().attr('src',videoURL);
        })
    });
       </script>
       <script id="jplayer-template-video" type="text/x-handlebars-template">
        <div class="video-container">
        <a href="{{link}}?wmode=transparent&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1">
            <img data-src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{videoID}}/mqdefault.jpg" class="wide" />
            <img data-src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/{{videoID}}/hqdefault.jpg" class="narrow" />
            <span class="ss-icon">&#x25B6;</span>
        </a>
        <iframe id="ytplayer{{id}}" type="text/html" width="640" height="390" src="" frameborder="0"/>
    </div>
       </script>

        <div class="jp-progress">

        </div>
        <ul class="jp-controls right">

          <li><a href="javascript:;" class="ss-icon jp-unmute" tabindex="1" title="unmute">&#x1F508;</a></li>

            <div class="jp-volume-bar">

      </div>

    function flexSliderDefer(method) { if (typeof jQuery.flexslider === "function") { method(); } else { setTimeout(function() { flexSliderDefer(method) }, 50); } }
    $(document).ready(function ()
    {

    function MediaArchive_EndRequestHandler(sender, args) {
        $('.media-item-image').closest('.media-item').addClass('hasTeaser');

    function startPlayers()
    {
        try
        {
            for (var i = 0; i < audioFunctions.length; i++)
            {
                makeJPlayer(audioFunctions[i][0], audioFunctions[i][1], audioFunctions[i][2], audioFunctions[i][3]);

            for (var j = 0; j < videoFunctions.length; j++)

    function initializeFlexy()
    {
        // Flexslider Initiation
        if($('#slideHolder'))
        {
            try
            {
                $('#slideHolder').flexslider({
                    animation: "slide",

                    prevText: "&#x25C5;",

                    start: function(slider) { $(slider).find('li.flex-active-slide img').unveil(200, function() {
                        $(this).load(function() { this.style.opacity = 1; });
                    }); },
                    before: function(slider) { $(slider).find('li.flex-active-slide img').unveil(200, function() {
                        $(this).load(function() { this.style.opacity = 1; });
                    }); },
                    after: function(slider) { $(slider).find('li.flex-active-slide img').unveil(200, function() {
                        $(this).load(function() { this.style.opacity = 1; });

        if($('#mobileSlideHolder'))

                        $(this).load(function() { this.style.opacity = 1; });
                    }); }
                });        
            }
            catch (e) 
            {
                  alert(e);
            }
        }
    }
